content.warning: Popeza pulogalamuyi imagwira ntchito yovomerezeka pafoni yanu yam'manja, zilolezo zambiri ndizowopsa kwambiri, chifukwa chake musalowe kapena kuwapha popanda kukwaniritsa zoopsa kapena zolembedwa. Mukayamba kulowa mu "Makalata Omaliza a Steaction" kapena "Bokosi Losakhazikika pa intaneti, zomwe zili pansipa zidzaphedwa nthawi yomweyo. Chonde khalani osamala.
